OL,5, Schools are spending tens of thousands 
OL,6, of pounds more a year to meet rising   
OL,7, costs of contracts with private firms. 
OL,9,FThese Private Finance Initiative (PFI) 
OL,10,Fschools are locked into 25- to 30-year 
OL,11,Fcontracts in which charges go up by the
OL,12,Fhighest measure of inflation.          
OL,14,FOne school said "rigid" and "specific" 
OL,15,Fdemands set out in its PFI contract now
OL,16,Fcost almost 20% of its budget.         
OL,18,FPFI investors say the contracts are    
OL,19,Flong-term value for money for          
OL,20,Ftaxpayers.                             
